step 2: configure the git bash with github details
step 3: create reppositary in the github
step 4: git init in the git bash
step 5: git status (check the status)
step 6: git add <filename>
step 7 : git status(check the status whether the files add or not)
step 8 : add the commands from the github repo

git commit -m "comment"
git push origin main


